<div data-type=3D"problem" id=3D"fs-idm43643408"><div class=3D"os-problem-c=
ontainer">
<p id=3D"fs-idm43925792">A trainer is teaching a rescued dolphin to catch l=
ive fish before returning it to the wild. The probability that the dolphin =
successfully catches a fish is 35%, and the probability that the dolphin do=
es not successfully catch the fish is 65%. Out of 20 attempts, you want to =
find the probability that the dolphin succeeds 12 times. State the probabil=
ity question mathematically.</p></div></div>
</section></div>
