</h2></header><section>
<div class=3D"os-note-body">
<div data-type=3D"exercise" id=3D"fs-idp231440" class=3D"unnumbered"><heade=
r></header><section>
<div data-type=3D"problem" id=3D"fs-idm386096"><div class=3D"os-problem-con=
tainer">
<p id=3D"fs-idm59210304">Sixty-five percent of people pass the state driver=
=E2=80=99s exam on the first try. A group of 50 individuals who have taken =
the driver=E2=80=99s exam is randomly selected. Give two reasons why this i=
s a binomial problem.</p></div></div>
</section></div>
