</h2></header><section>
<div class=3D"body">
<p id=3D"fs-idm124136240">The lifetime risk of developing cancer is about o=
ne in 67 (1.5%). Suppose we randomly sample 200 people. Let <em data-effect=
=3D"italics">X</em> =3D the number of people who will develop cancer.</p><d=
iv data-type=3D"exercise" id=3D"fs-idm129798576" class=3D"unnumbered has-pr=
oblem-title"><header></header><section>
<div data-type=3D"problem" id=3D"fs-idm14459520"><h3 data-type=3D"problem-t=
itle">
