</h3>
<div class=3D"os-problem-container">
<ol id=3D"fs-idm74773968" type=3D"a">
<li>What is the probability distribution for <em data-effect=3D"italics">X<=
/em>?</li>
<li>Using the formulas, calculate the (i) mean and (ii) standard deviation =
of <em data-effect=3D"italics">X</em>.</li>
<li>Use your calculator to find the probability that at most eight people d=
evelop cancer</li>
<li>Is it more likely that five or six people will develop cancer? Justify =
your answer numerically.</li>
</ol></div></div>
